flavorText: The earth shook in support of their cause, offering a champion of its own.
name: Primeval Protector

rulings.text: Once a player has announced that they are casting Primeval Protector, no player may take actions to try to change the number of creatures your opponents control in order to increase its cost.
Primeval Protector's ability can't reduce its cost below {G}.

text:
This spell costs {1} less to cast for each creature your opponents control.
When Primeval Protector enters the battlefield, put a +1/+1 counter on each other creature you control.
